data.description: ABSOLUTELY STUNNING REMODELED POOL HOME!  4 Bedrooms and 3 Bathrooms located on a wonderful Cul-de-sac street in a highly sought-after Lake Forest community. TURNKEY PROPERTY with extravagant flooring, remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, and exquisite cabinetry. Enjoy meals together in the Chef’s Kitchen with island. Built-in luxurious cabinetry in kitchen with glass doors. High vaulted ceilings greet you at the entrance. Beveled glass door at your front door. Fabulous staircase with wrought iron. One bedroom downstairs is currently being used as an office. Expansive family room; great place to enjoy watching movies and football games together. On the second floor you will additionally find 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 beautiful remodeled bathrooms. Dual Pane windows and plantation shutters. Downstairs bathroom has been remodeled with granite countertop vanity and shower with decorative tile. It’s PARTY TIME to have fun in YOUR POOL and ENTERTAINER’S BACKYARD with guests & family. Covered patio with ceiling fans. Built-in-BBQ perfect for grilling. Front yard at entrance has a pleasurable courtyard for sitting by the firepit. Enjoy Lake Forest Sail Club for swimming, sailing, tennis, basketball, plus more!  Get ready for many new adventures! Centrally location near shopping, entertaiment, great restaurants & easy access to 5 highway. START PACKING!!!
